2003-02-13 16:44  tomp

	* src/: input/ParButtonModule.cxx, misc/PortTalk_IOCTL.h,
	misc/pt_ioctl.c:
	
	new version of ParButtonModule uses PortTalk2.2

2003-02-07 17:41  flo

	* src/input/: SpeechModule.cxx, SpeechModule.h:
	
	moved implementation of Speak() method from headerfile (inline)  to
	cxx file  - this causes an linker error when linking stbapi in
	release configuration.	i think it is bad practice to specify
	methods that use non-local information or calls as inline...

